	<h1 class="title">建筑家的野心又一例，弗兰克·盖里想改造洛杉矶运河</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/37534/small/37534.JPG?1421809836" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">石玉 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-08-11 13:13:09 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/13334/medium/13334.jpg?1439261882" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


